Running command: . ~/.nvm/nvm.sh; opencode --model=onprem/models/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-FP8 run --format=json --thinking --dangerously-skip-permissions -- 'You are implementing a **fused GPU kernel** that combines a **communication op**
